data.name: label7.Text
data.value:
Here, User can interact with a realistic network topology:
- User can Find the best route from one node to another - User can view the current topology in the adjacency matrix - User can manipulate the weight of each link - User can disable any node at will by "clicking on the node" - User can choose to randomize the weight on all the link - User can save the current weight and continue on the next login
